<section id="about" class="relative py-32 md:py-40">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1200px] px-6">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 md:gap-16 items-start">
      <!-- Left label -->
      <div class="md:col-span-4" data-animate>
        <span class="text-xs font-mono text-text-muted tracking-widest uppercase block mb-4">
          01 — About
        </span>
        <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-tight">
          Engineering<br />
          <span class="gradient-text">with intent</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <!-- Right content -->
      <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-6">
        <p data-animate data-animate-delay="1" class="text-lg text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Terminus Labs is a software development and consulting firm built on the
          belief that great software is a competitive advantage. We work closely with
          our clients to understand their business goals and translate them into
          reliable, well-architected systems.
        </p>
        <p data-animate data-animate-delay="2" class="text-lg text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Founded by an engineer who's shipped products across industries —
          from enterprise SaaS platforms and mobile apps to niche vertical
          software — we bring deep full-stack expertise paired with a pragmatic,
          results-driven approach. Every decision — from architecture to
          deployment — is made with long-term maintainability in mind.
        </p>
        <p data-animate data-animate-delay="3" class="text-lg text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          We don't believe in one-size-fits-all solutions. Whether you need a
          full-stack web application, a complex API integration, or strategic
          technical guidance — we adapt our approach to fit the problem, not the
          other way around.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
